description: Reserved matters application pursuant to 12/00210/0UT (as amended by 15/00337/VAR) for siting, design, external appearance of the building and the landscaping for Phase 3, which comprises three buildings (blocks O, P and Q) which range in height from 6 to 8 storeys and contain 525 sqm of commercial space at ground and mezzanine floor and 93 dwellings, along landscaped space, with refuse / recycling facilities and cycle parking.
